txt.en: Orc barricades and supplies for battle can be found at Mokh Shapat in Arandor.\n\nYou should destroy supplies and Orc barricades at Mokh Shapat.
Orc barricades and supplies for battle can be found at Mokh Shapat in Arandor.\n\nYou should destroy supplies and Orc barricades at Mokh Shapat.
Destroy supplies and Orc barricades at Mokh Shapat

The Orc encampment of Mokh Shapat is protected by crude barricades. Within, foes of the Great Alliance have stocked the camp with supplies and weapons that will be put to evil use. These barricades and provisions must be destroyed.
You destroyed many barricades and supplies at the Orc encampment of Mokh Shapat, which will weaken their ability to do battle with the soldiers of the Great Alliance.
Destroyed many barricades and supplies at Mokh Shapat.
Many Orcs and beasts under the command of Sauron gather at the encampment of Mokh Shapat.
